    apt-get install libudev-dev libusb-1.0-0-dev libfox-1.6-dev



  Then you need to get hidapi from http://www.signal11.us/oss/hidapi/
  The easiest way to get this if you have git is:
  
      git clone git://github.com/signal11/hidapi.git


./bootstrap
	./configure
	make
	make install     <----- as root, or using sudo




sudo    /sbin/udevadm control --reload-rules


NOW you are ready to compile the MCC libusb programs
   tar zxvf  MCCLIBUSB.1.6.tgz  (or the latest version).
   cd mcc-libusb
   make
   sudo make install
   ldconfig 












